title: Chat with OpenAI CEO and and Co-founder Sam Altman, and Chief Scientist Ilya Sutskever
description:
Join Prof. Nadav Cohen from Tel Aviv University's Blavatnik School of Computer Science in this captivating conversation featuring Sam Altman, CEO of OpenAI, and the company's co-founder and chief scientist, Ilya Sutskever. Gain insights from these influential leaders as they discuss various thought-provoking topics, including:

- Exploring the opportunities and risks associated with AI
- Understanding the crucial role of academia in shaping AI advancements
- Unleashing the potential of AI to drive scientific and technological breakthroughs
- Addressing the necessity for effective regulation in the field
- Gaining valuable guidance on relevant areas of study for long-term job market relevance
- Unveiling insights on entrepreneurship in the dynamic landscape of 2023

Prepare to be inspired and enlightened as Altman and Sutskever dive deep into these subjects, followed by engaging Q&A sessions with the audience.
